query:
INSERT INTO userCoupons (userId, templateId, status, expireAt, createdAt)
SELECT 2, id, 'available', DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL validDays DAY), NOW()
FROM couponTemplates
WHERE isActive = 1
ORDER BY id
LIMIT 3;
